<view class='index'>
  <view class='header'>
    <view class='img'>
      <image src='http://llwell-wxapp.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/PurchasingAssistantPersonal/shop_img_rebate@3x.png'></image>
    </view>
    <view class='text'>
      <text class='h1'>Takarado宝堂</text>
      <text class='h2'>TAKARADO宝堂  是专注于为海淘达人们提供全球O2O跨境商品的旺铺。我们以“专注、专业、高效”为原则，严选全球的精致品牌商品，提供“品牌多、规格全、品类丰富”的100%跨境正品。</text>
      <view class='h3'>地址：仁川市机场路3号 <image src='http://llwell-wxapp.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/PurchasingAssistantPersonal/shop_icon_location@3x.png'></image></view>
      <view class='h4'>联系电话：34123243123 <image src='http://llwell-wxapp.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/PurchasingAssistantPersonal/shop_icon_phone@3x.png'></image></view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='content'>
    <view class='content_wrap' wx:for='{{List}}' data-index='{{index}}' key='{{index}}'>
      <view class='content_wrapLeft'>
        <image src='{{item.logo}}'></image>
      </view>
      <view class='content_wrapCenter'>
        <text class='content_brand'>{{item.name}}</text>
        <text class='content_num'>{{item.num}}个商品</text>
      </view>
      <view class='content_wrapRight'>
          <view><image src='{{item.hand}}'></image>{{item.recommend}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  
</view>